author: Lobo_da_boss_
title: Nice keyring
review:
Opening;

The batgirl keyring is a cool one as it is based of a minifigure that was exclusive to one 2014 DC superheroes set .

The Minifigure-

The figure is nice as it has the exclusive cowl hair combo from the set , a nice exclusive face print , a lovely lavender cape , an accurate torso print and plain black legs .

In conclusion-

this is my third favourite keyring in my collection just behind the gingerbread man and the BB9-E . I would recommend this to Batman fans but I do believe it is retired .
